structure.name: Personal income tax - central government rates and thresholds for a single person at 100% of average wage without dependents

names.en: Personal income tax - central government rates and thresholds for a single person at 100% of average wage without dependents

structure.description: This table reports statutory central government personal income tax rates for wage income plus the taxable income thresholds at which these statutory rates apply, including basic/standard tax allowances, tax credits and surtax rates. The information is applicable to a single person with no dependents.
